\description{
A general family implementing distributional regression for a circular
(angular) response \eqn{y} in radians under the cardioid law
\deqn{f(y) = \frac{1}{2\pi}\left(1 + 2\rho\cos(y - \mu)\right),
  \qquad 0 \le \rho \le 1/2,}
